---
/**
 * Full-width cinematic testimonial with photo background.
 * Single impactful quote -- not a card carousel.
 */
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden py-32">
  <!-- Background image -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <img
      src="/images/shop-1.jpg"
      alt="Voelz Body Shop"
      class="h-full w-full object-cover"
      loading="lazy"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-navy/85"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 text-center lg:px-12">
    <div class="scale-reveal">
      <!-- Large quote mark -->
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="mx-auto mb-8 h-12 w-12 text-primary/60" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10H14.017zM0 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151C7.546 6.068 5.983 8.789 5.983 11H10v10H0z" />
      </svg>

      <blockquote class="font-display text-2xl font-medium leading-relaxed text-white md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl">
        They did an outstanding job on my car after a bad accident. You can't even tell it was ever damaged. Honest, fair, and they kept me updated every step of the way.
      </blockquote>

      <div class="mt-10">
        <div class="mx-auto h-px w-16 bg-primary"></div>
        <p class="mt-6 font-display text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-primary">Satisfied Customer</p>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-400">Yelp Review</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
